data.description: Short Sale. Price Cut!!! Come see this 5 bed  3.5 bath home in a great, sought after area with fantastic Seminole county schools.   Home boasts an interior in-law suite with built in separate full kitchen, living room with a bay window and separate backyard access, a bedroom and en-suite bathroom.     4 beds and 2.5 baths throughout the rest of the house with two optional living rooms/study.  Fenced backyard and screened in Lanai. NO HOA, PLUS one house away is optional lakefront community lot- $50/year SPRING FED BEAR LAKE COMMUNITY LOT USE/ACCESS WITH BOAT RAMP! Easy access to all Orlando metro has to offer. Close to 436, 429/414 toll roads and I-4.     Come see it!
